<item>
            <title>[LU-8153] lustre-ppc build failed since 2016-04-04</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8153</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It appears that lustre-ppc builds have been failing since 2016-04-04, the last successful build was &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/lustre-ppc/437/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/lustre-ppc/437/&lt;/a&gt; (May 14, 2016 16:07:12).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It appears to be failing during configure, but I haven&apos;t looked into the details.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;checking for external module build target... M
checking that modules can be built at all... no
configure: error: 

Kernel modules cannot be built. Consult config.log for details.

If you are trying to build with a kernel-source rpm,
consult build/README.kernel-source
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
